  <h2>The Ith-Region</h2>
  <p>The <strong>Ith-Region</strong> is a partnership between the towns of <strong>Salzhemmendorf</strong> and <strong>Coppenbrügge</strong> in the eastern Weserbergland, Lower Saxony. Together, we are developing a nature-oriented, active and cooperatively organised tourism region.</p>

  <h3>Our Vision</h3>
  <p>The Ith-Region positions itself as a <strong>nature-oriented, active and authentic holiday destination</strong> offering recreation, regional culture and active experiences – for guests and locals alike.</p>

  <h3>Cooperation</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Joint marketing under the <strong>"Ith-Region"</strong> brand</li>
    <li>Development of shared offerings with local tourism businesses</li>
    <li>Partnership with <strong>Weserbergland Tourism</strong> association</li>
  </ul>

  <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-ith-teal bg-ith-teal/5 p-6 rounded-r-xl my-8">
    <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-ith-blue-dark italic">"Every Path is Your Adventure"</p>
  </blockquote>
